ygData.messageBody:
I don't know what happened but I cant seem to get into the game anymore.
After I select my guy, I hit enter world and then after about a minute, I
get the 'Server not responding" message. I have reinstalled and repatched
the game. Changed my settings for my video and sound cards and a half a
dozen other things. Frankly I have ran out of ideas. Any help here will be
greatly appreciated. I want my EQ!!! My friend has already leveld past me
and we can;t have that can we?
